Increase the amount of woodland in the UK from 12% to 50%.

If you really think the environment is less important than money, try holding your breath while you count your money.

There are many other benefits of planting new woodland – here are just some of them:

•	give wildlife a helping hand
•	create beautiful places for people
•	support the environment
•	remove poisonous gasses and provide oxygen
•	enhance local business
•	grow cover for game
•	improve property values.

Finland and Sweden are amongst the highest with 68%+

Germany has 35%.
